name: KINQ (KINGOFSTX)
description: The purpose of our project: To provide community support to the developing stx ecosystem by taking advantage of the development of the stx network and to draw attention to the stx network. As in every network, it aims to be at the top by creating a fun and original community. It is ready to take the necessary steps to provide these conditions and continues its work. The project prioritizes receiving trust-based transactions. For this reason, it has preferred a constantly developing and growing network. Being a part of the Bitcoin ecosystem is one of the main goals of the project. Developments prove the accuracy of this decision.
